    "name": "Bubsy in: The Purrfect Collection",
    "steam_appid": 3039890,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >山猫Bubsy，究竟是上世纪90年代初吉祥物大战中的传奇巨星，还是平台跳跃游戏界的笑柄？Limited Run Games团队全新打造的合集将揭晓答案。《Bubs+ in: The Purrfect Collection》探索了该系列坎坷的历史和经久不衰的人气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039890/extras/2913e7dbd62ab5e3b287fce15dfc22a8.poster.avif?t=1757692284\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039890/extras/2913e7dbd62ab5e3b287fce15dfc22a8.webm?t=1757692284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Bubsy in: The Purrfect Collection》以充满可玩性的游戏发展时间线呈现，收录了系列作品、珍贵资料与开发者访谈，所有游戏均采用Limited Run独家Carbon引擎，并为现代平台精心优化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039890/extras/67d6a178eb5d3ffebbc661e8ba33d8ac.poster.avif?t=1757692284\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039890/extras/67d6a178eb5d3ffebbc661e8ba33d8ac.webm?t=1757692284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该项目由Audi Sorlie领衔，这位制作人、作家兼“Bubsy世界重量级冠军”堪称该游戏系列的头号专家。他与Limited Run及雅达利团队联手，为这只身高1米、体重36公斤的山猫打造了一场终极怀旧盛宴。这样的游戏怎么会不好玩呢？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收录作品：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 《Bubsy in: Claws Encounters of the Furred Kind》（Super Nintendo Entertainment System™, Super Famicom™, SEGA Genesis™）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 《Bubsy II》（Super Nintendo Entertainment System™, SEGA Genesis™, Game Boy™）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 《Bubsy in: Fractured Furry Tales》（Atari Jaguar™）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 《Bubsy 3D》（PlayStation®）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039890/extras/0bf7d57fb8b7e4b837dd575af11f40bc.poster.avif?t=1757692284\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039890/extras/0bf7d57fb8b7e4b837dd575af11f40bc.webm?t=1757692284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 收录的每款作品均支持画质帧数与分辨率增强，配备即时存档与回档功能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 首度公开的绝密档案：原画设定、说明书、广告等高清扫描件</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 深度访谈影片揭秘游戏史上最声名狼藉的山猫及其开发历程</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 专属音乐播放器畅听经典曲目</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039890/extras/4924e89fd579465a9cd87eaa8f0554f1.poster.avif?t=1757692284\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039890/extras/4924e89fd579465a9cd87eaa8f0554f1.webm?t=1757692284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039890/extras/4924e89fd579465a9cd87eaa8f0554f1.mp4?t=1757692284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
